Christ Apostolic Church, Mount of Blessing, Alagomeji, Yaba, Lagos State, is set to celebrate its 79th anniversary with a weeklong programme. The programme, which is to honour members of the church from 70 and above, is divided  into three – Gold (90 and above), silver (80 to 89) and bronze (70 to 89). According to the committees for the celebration, the  church decided to honour  the Senior Citizens  to appreciate them for their selfless service, dedication and contributions to the progress and development of the church. The programme  will also feature a symposium, film and crusade on October 20.